  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1020080/extras/e8999c9e11a1b950107f011e7cde936e.avif?t=1572516243\" width=614 height=92 /></span></h2>Turns out that Da Vinci has invented the time machine! However, things didn’t go as planned with the new invention.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1020080/extras/786d8da814cc6aa6c2fed7605ed4ca14.avif?t=1572516243\" width=614 height=181 /></span></h2>Due to an error in calculations, Da Vinci’s loved one - Cecilia - was sent back in time! In an attempt to rescue the woman he loves, Da Vinci decided to follow her, but accidentally travelled to the future.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1020080/extras/810fddc3fd304fba6bacbfe793de518d.avif?t=1572516243\" width=614 height=181 /></span></h2>It’s not too late to undo the damage, but the great scientist will need help from Alicia Quatermain! The duo will travel across time and space and visit mythical places!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1020080/extras/942fa8b550696b43bbc4c3dc4a217c3d.avif?t=1572516243\" width=614 height=181 /></span></h2>Can Alicia and Leonardo Da Vinci save Cecilia and prevent the time travel disaster?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1020080/extras/4f822a420ea0ada5b7318eca4b5af73b.avif?t=1572516243\" width=614 height=181 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Interactive guide! <br></li><li> Wallpapers!<br></li><li> Additional bonus levels<br></li><li> Alicia Quatermain’s adventures continue<br></li><li> Stunning full HD graphics<br></li><li> Special challenges for skilled players on difficult mode<br></li><li> A fascinating plot and interesting characters<br></li><li> Puzzles and bonus levels for the attentive players<br></li><li> A chance to save the rare relict</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1020080/extras/fbcbc90ca1f3a1b7f9eea4eee18a9e69.avif?t=1572516243\" width=614 height=152 /></span></h2>",
